data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home on corner lot on cul-de-sac! Welcome to the River Falls community.  This one has endless possibilities with tons of space, natural light and several living/flex areas.  Large kitchen has new stainless steel oven and microwave. Primary suite has impressive retreat/sitting area with nicely sized bathroom with garden tub and separate shower.  Step outside and enjoy a private, fenced backyard with nice landscaping. Double car garage with side entry makes this one even more appealing.  Don't miss this one.
